abstract: >
  Reproducible Python laboratories associated with the publication
  Factual entropy and structural irreversibility in the Sistema Vectorial SV:
  pre-ternary dispersion, transport law along the foundational chain and
  asymmetric conservation of factual content. The package verifies the
  pre-ternary dispersion, factual entropy monotonicity, consistency walk,
  simulated retroactive violation and three canonical dictum examples.
  The main documentary Commons/KCWorks publication DOI is 10.17613/vh6ak-6em43.
